text: Abdul Hafeez Khan is an Indian politician . He has been a member of the YSR Congress Party since 2011. When he returned to India, Y.S.Jagan Mohan Reddy invited him to hoist the party flag in Kurnool. He represented Kurnool in the 2019 Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly election gaining 72,819 votes representing a 47.70% share of the vote in the constituency. == References == Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:YSR Congress politicians
